positive.valid_data: when user input data api create kyc using valid data, then user got response 200/ok

negative.maxDob: when user input data api create kyc using max dob(55th 181hr), then user got response error
negative.minDob: when user input data api create kyc using min dob(17th 180hr), then user got response error
negative.maxKtp: when user input data api create kyc using max dob(more than 16 digit), then user got response error
negative.minKtp: when user input data api create kyc using min dob(less than 16 digit), then user got response error
